Please use CMake to build.

mkdir build
cmake -DCMAKE_CXX_COMPILER=clang++ -DCMAKE_C_COMPILER=clang ..
make -j4



------------
all builds require llvm/clang >= 3.4 for full C++11 standard support
along with a compatible C++ STL implementation. all makefiles are
adjusted to use the GNU STL libc++. all builds tested and working
with libc++ version >= 4.7.2.5-5
------------